# component

component.* describes the component system used in <name> to seperate and manage the different systems in <name>.

## Classes

### BaseComponent
#### Description
This is the base component. It contains common data required by almost all other components, such as position or *.

#### Functions

### VAO
#### Description
This is a basic rendering component. It contains all the OpenGL required to render a mesh, provided during construction. It is managed by a GLProgram, which contains the OpenGL shaders etc.

